The game is divided in three rooms Silver Gold and Platinum from which you have select any one according to your wallet budget and prediction skills.Taxaal is world class 24 X 7 prediction game.Its 100% legal safe secure.It features free registration instant wallet recharge fast withdrawls.So !!! Start Predicting and win Prediction Hints Hi !!!! You feel you are good at predictions.So Great news for you.Your prediction skills can make you win exciting prizes.Taxaal - The Predict and Win Game is the right place for you.Taxaal announces a lucky number in every 15 minutes.You have to predict number ranging from 0 to 9 by applying Taxaal coins on either single or multiple numbers.If your prediction match with the lucky number declared then you will recieve 9 times the amount you used on that respective number. Say you have used 100 coins on number 1 200 on number 3 and 150 on number 8 and the lucky number announced is 3 then u will get 1800 coins back in the Taxaal wallet. The more you predict more you win . Taxaal - About
